                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "Yes, the B230FIZC is highly tunable. Common upgrades include a manual boost controller, a performance exhaust, and ECU chip tuning. More significant power gains can be achieved by upgrading the fuel injectors, installing a larger turbocharger, and fitting a front-mount intercooler, though this requires supporting modifications and careful tuning.",
